nroffed_file ({0,2,9,"rearrange","Discworld player help","rearrange","Name",7,5,"rearrange - Rearrange your stats.","Syntax",7,5,"rearrange","Description",3,5,5,"You are able to configure your character once.  You will be allowed once during your characters life to modify the stats that you start with.  Stats take the range of 8 -> 18/00 normally.  You can make your stats what you want them to be by typing rearrange and following the instructions.  The idea of this command is to make your character what you want it to be.  You should also read the help on stats to find out what each of them does.  Don't play with this until you have decided what you want your character to be like. ","See also",7,5,"score.",})
